The Natural Solution for Better Sex, Better Sleep and More Energy

Learn the secrets of 50 herbs that will improve your sex life, sleep and energy levels.

Let 50 Shades of Herbs turn you on and pump you up! In this book you will learn:

How Natural Herbal Remedies Can Improve Your Sex Life Without Harmful Side Effects

In just a few moments, you're about to learn how powerful herbs like the amazing Maca Root (Peruvian Viagra), Horny Goat Weed (Yin Yang Huo), and Cnidium Monnier (The Natural Libido Booster), and many more can help improve your circulation, metabolism, libido, and rev up your sex life naturally!

How To Get Better Sleep (With or Without Sex)

You'll also learn about 10 life-changing herbs that can help you get better sleep, have more energy and feel better all day long. Some of these calming and soothing herbs have been used for thousands of years, and now you too can benefit from these powerful natural remedies. If you have trouble sleeping, this chapter alone could change your life!
